queries.sql: SELECT investments.*, users.fullname, users.company, SUM(reports.cost) as total_cost, (investments.cost - SUM(reports.cost)) as cost_left FROM investments JOIN users on investments.client_id = users.id JOIN reports ON reports.investment_id = investments.id WHERE users.role = 'client' AND status = 'incomplete' GROUP BY reports.investment_id ORDER BY status DESC, cost_left ASC

timelineData.query: SELECT investments.*, users.fullname, users.company, SUM(reports.cost) as total_cost, (investments.cost - SUM(reports.cost)) as cost_left FROM investments JOIN users on investments.client_id = users.id JOIN reports ON reports.investment_id = investments.id WHERE users.role = 'client' AND status = 'incomplete' GROUP BY reports.investment_id ORDER BY status DESC, cost_left ASC
